posts.body:
I came here for this thread.

How do I grind willpower?

I dont understand how to seed either.
Do I just need to add the site to favorites? Is it per board? Per file? Per post?
I dont understand, but am loving it.

Am staying.
Though I think that the same way I found this website, others will, and we will soon have the same problem of too many people shitposting and drowning real discussion.
For now, though? This place is cozy.

I don't think this is any safer from glowniggers, though. It only took me 10 seconds of browsing zerosites to find a cp site, which is probably a honeypot. I dont really care since I was behind 7 proxies, but I imagine that alphabet agencies will be just as present here as they were on clearnet chans.
We will have less shills hopefully, though.

So is this the /fringe/ bunker?
Any 0net fringe study websites?
